  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Cook",
  "description": "<h2>Cook (Full-Time / Part-Time)</h2><p><strong>Location:</strong> Orchard Road – Peranakan Restaurant</p><p>We are looking for passionate and reliable Cooks to join our Peranakan kitchen team. If you enjoy cooking, learning heritage recipes, and working in a supportive environment, we’d love to meet you.</p><h3>Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Prepare and cook Peranakan dishes according to recipes and standards</p></li><li><p>Assist with food prep, plating, and kitchen operations</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and food hygiene in the kitchen</p></li><li><p>Support the team during service hours</p></li><li><p>Follow kitchen SOPs and safety guidelines</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Basic cooking experience preferred (training provided)</p></li><li><p>Willingness to learn Peranakan cuisine</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude and team spirit</p></li><li><p>Able to stand for long hours and work in a fast-paced kitchen</p></li><li><p>Responsible and punctual</p></li></ul><h3>Working Arrangements</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Full-Time:</strong> 5–6 days per week</p></li><li><p><strong>Part-Time:</strong> Flexible shifts available</p></li></ul><p>✨ We welcome mature workers, caregivers, and those returning to work. On-the-job training provided.<br /><br />If interested to apply, kindly whatsapp 9067 4216. Thank you</p>",
